Instruction

Write a query to find the top 3 film categories that generated the most sales.
The order of your results doesn't matter.
Table: sales_by_film_category
Total sales by movie categories.

  col_name   | col_type
-------------+----------
 category    | text
 total_sales | numeric
Sample results

category
-----------
Category 1
Category 2
Category 3




SELECT category FROM sales_by_film_category
ORDER BY total_sales
DESC
LIMIT 3 OFFSET 0




category
Sports
Sci-Fi
Animation
